path.id: You spend 5 minutes to read the comic, while not every investor could stick with one company for 5 years.

Your trading times is limitted only 4 times during the 5 years. While many investors claim themselves as long-term investors, but they tend to withdraw money for fear of additional losses when the price just begin to drop.
Congrats! With $ earned in the market, you have $ in total.
Just as Warren Buffett said, The stock market is designed to transfer money from the active to the patient..... good luck!

According to Dalbar in its 26th Annual Quantitative Analysis of Investor Behavior study, which covers the 20-year period to December 31, 2019, 70% of average investor underperformance happened during 10 key periods of market crisis when they took action (buying or selling), instead of staying the course.
While many of these same investors fail to buy in when a rebound occurs, and jump back in only when most of the gains have already been achieved.
